profile_positions.description:
In 2010 I joined Energy Business as a junior cost engineering manager. In 2011 I was appointed product manager focusing on rooftop PV solar projects. Also, I was part of a business diversification project with LED lights. 

•	PV: Managed projects ensuring delivery in a cross-functional team environment (engineers, KAMs, lawyer, notary, consultants); Business development and stakeholders engagement activity with national and foreign customers;
•	LED: market intelligence, feasibility and profitability analysis, suppliers’ benchmark study, value proposition to customers and sales activity with Italian, Chinese and German customers.
